video_title: Do You Struggle with Finding Affordable Mental Health Treatment? #mentalhealth
transcript:
did you guys know that about four out of
10 Americans cannot afford mental health
treatment in the United States according
to the National Council for mental
well-being 42% of us adults who needed
care in the previous 12 months were
unable to get it due to high costs here
at Psy too we're passionate about
advocating for accessible mental health
education and treatment join us on
October 14th at Barnes & Noble to
fundraise for the nurus Clinic
Foundation an amazing nonprofit that
makes mental healthc care more
affordable and accessible in the
community if you can't make it you can
always donate by clicking on the
Eventbrite link and part of the proceeds
will go to the narus clinic hope to see
you all
there
